room_title: Escape room "The Honor Roll" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: Shout Out to Matt Smiley and Liberation Escape Rooms. They went above and beyond to accommodate our family on my son's 16th Birthday. The family had an awesome time outsmarting Billy the Bully in Honor Roll. We will definitely be back.
